---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="DMCA Takedown — Fimil"
  description="Copyright infringement notification process for the Fimil platform."
>
  <article class="py-20 dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/legal" class="text-sm text-fimil-600 hover:text-fimil-700 dark:text-fimil-400"
        >&larr; Legal</a
      >
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        DMCA Takedown Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            1. Reporting Copyright Infringement
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you believe content on the Fimil platform infringes your copyright, submit a DMCA
            takedown notice to <a
              href="mailto:legal@fimil.dev"
              class="text-fimil-600 dark:text-fimil-400">legal@fimil.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            2. Required Information
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Your notice must include: identification of the copyrighted work, the infringing
            material and its location, your contact information, a good faith statement, a statement
            of accuracy under penalty of perjury, and your physical or electronic signature.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            3. Counter-Notification
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you believe content was removed in error, you may submit a counter-notification with
            the required information under the DMCA.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            4. Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            DMCA Agent: <a href="mailto:legal@fimil.dev" class="text-fimil-600 dark:text-fimil-400"
              >legal@fimil.dev</a
            >
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
